snippet.title: Hearthstone | TITANS Announcement
snippet.description:
Join Game Designers, Alex Smith and Edward Goodwin, as they explain what’s new to Hearthstone in the latest expansion. TITANS will launch worldwide on August 1, with a 145-card expansion that includes Legendary Titans and Keepers, new Signature card looks, the new Forge keyword, the returning Magnetic keyword, and more! 

Pre Purchase TITANS Mega Bundle: https://blizz.ly/46rHvuU
Learn more about TITANS: https://blizz.ly/43SyLMw
Read the 26.6 Patch Notes: https://blizz.ly/3NnnWv0
TITANS Card Library: https://blizz.ly/3Nq4AoT

http://PlayHearthstone.com
